title: Carol/Jess Mini Bang Art Claims
body:
Art claims for the Carol/Jess mini bang are now open!

To claim one of the stories please fill out the form here.

To read the summaries and check codenames, please see here.

If you didn’t sign up as an artist but are interested in making a piece of art for one of the stories, please feel free to fill out the claim form. If a story you choose goes unclaimed, or if all stories get claimed at least once, we will contact you about participating.

summary: Brie Larson Confirms Captain Marvel Has Finished Filming
title: Brie Larson Confirms Captain Marvel Has Finished Filming
body:
Brie Larson Confirms Captain Marvel Has Finished Filming

It’s official folks, Marvel’s, Captain Marvelhas officially finished filming as confirmed by lead actress Brie Larson. The female power is growing with this epic film, set to release next year and I couldn’t be more excited.

Larson shared on Twitter:

https://twitter.com/brielarson/status/1016058456061558784

That is one cool looking clapboard if you ask me. Look at all of those lovely signatures.…

tags: I just really need 100% confirmation that Billy will be written well.
If he is then I can forgive a lot.
summary: Billy is assigned to a new foster home where he befriends comic book superfan Freddy. One day, Billy’s subway ride is...
body:
Billy is assigned to a new foster home where he befriends comic book superfan Freddy. One day, Billy’s subway ride is interrupted by a mysterious Wizard whose been searching for ages to find the right successor to inherit his powers. He reveals the teen’s been selected to gain an assortment of abilities, and all it takes is for Billy to say “SHAZAM!”

Maybe I’m reading too much into it, but I like that this says that Billy’s “been selected.” On its face, this means that yes, the Wizard has already deemed him worthy, which means that no, he’s not a little jerk who only gets the powers because the Wizard decided to settle.
